WEBVTT

00:00:00.800 --> 00:00:06.848
Ready. Hey, good morning family. Praise the Lord. Thank you for joining us again today.

00:00:06.849 --> 00:00:10.879
We're excited to be here. We have some things on our heart to pray about.

00:00:10.880 --> 00:00:17.765
There are so many of you already here is what I want to say, but we're excited to see you all.

00:00:17.766 --> 00:00:23.912
We went to a Billy Burke healing service this week. That's where we were.

00:00:23.913 --> 00:00:28.636
If everybody wanted to know, they're like, "How come you're not posting videos?"Well, we're getting refreshed.

00:00:28.637 --> 00:00:38.666
And we went down to Fort Worth to see Billy Burke, and it was wonderful. You know, we had great expectations. We did.

00:00:38.667 --> 00:00:46.914
I told her, "Man, I cannot wait to go."The first night when we went, we saw so many of you all.

00:00:46.915 --> 00:00:55.274
I mean, there were so many people that came from all over the United States to say hello to us and come to the service and everything.

00:00:55.275 --> 00:01:11.234
So, you know, with me and Diana, I told her, I said, "I'm not used to being in public and people knowing who I am, especially in a church that's that big."Everybody came up trying to introduce themselves.

00:01:11.235 --> 00:01:17.954
I'm a person who is already discerning; I'm trying to see if you're a friend or a foe.

00:01:17.955 --> 00:01:24.943
Are you here to be nice to me, or are you going to come against me? So I'm looking at people's eyes.

00:01:24.944 --> 00:01:35.677
When there are that many coming, and it's that much of a flood, and I'm having that much of a download trying to find—I told Braden, "That was really awkward,"because I'm not used to that.

00:01:35.678 --> 00:01:45.993
Trying to shake everybody's hand and discern what's going on with them, I told Diana, "I'm going to have to practice a lot because I'm not used to it."We're hermits, y'all.

00:01:45.995 --> 00:01:55.457
We stay at home a lot because of our daughter. You know, she has special needs she's overcoming, so I'm not used to going out and being in a big crowd like that.

00:01:55.458 --> 00:02:02.611
Our little church that we have there in Collinsville only has probably four or five hundred people there on a Sunday.

00:02:02.612 --> 00:02:10.363
But when you have thousands of people in an auditorium, it's a big difference for us. But it was so nice to meet you all.

00:02:10.364 --> 00:02:17.696
And I want to say, if you're there, I know it's exciting to see us, but I want to tell you, we're just Brandon and Diana.

00:02:17.697 --> 00:02:21.809
We appreciate all the honor, and we pray for every single one of you if you want prayer.

00:02:21.810 --> 00:02:30.916
But like I said, there were so many people at one time, I told her, "I don't know how to do that next time,"trying to go through everything.

00:02:30.917 --> 00:02:43.648
But if you came out there and we prayed for you, where I'm going with that is: if you got prayer and you were in that service, did you receive your healing?

00:02:43.649 --> 00:02:47.110
I'm excited to hear, because there were some people that had strokes, folks.

00:02:47.111 --> 00:02:53.830
And there were some people battling depression and all kinds of different things that they were going through that they needed a miracle.

00:02:53.831 --> 00:03:01.754
They needed a breakthrough in their life. It was exciting to see them. I'm believing that they got touched.

00:03:01.755 --> 00:03:11.505
There was one lady, folks, who got touched so much that she could hardly drive home, and she was supposed to help navigate her husband clear back to Austin, Texas.

00:03:11.506 --> 00:03:20.677
And she didn't know—she was like she was on another planet. I'm talking about, she had the Holy Ghost all over her.

00:03:20.678 --> 00:03:25.216
It was amazing, wasn't it? Yeah. And really nice people from Estonia.

00:03:25.217 --> 00:03:33.070
Is that right? Estonia. Braden remembers. But like I said, there were people coming from everywhere.

00:03:33.071 --> 00:03:36.708
But I just wanted to say thank you all, always, for being so kind.

00:03:36.709 --> 00:03:44.599
To the people from Houston I met who had an air duct system business, they're such a blessing, and we pray over them and so many people.

00:03:44.600 --> 00:03:50.120
We met the people with the dogs, you know, so it was really interesting.

00:03:50.121 --> 00:03:57.779
It's kind of like our public debut in a sense, since the ministry is really growing, to go out and meet everybody.

00:03:57.780 --> 00:04:10.613
But I want to keep kicking that down the road. I mean, we can go over things, but one of the things is really cool. Now, I have to go back. Let me back it up a little bit.

00:04:10.614 --> 00:04:22.305
As we were sitting in the back—because the Lord told me, before all this happened, on Wednesday before we left, I was overcoming big time and I was under attack.

00:04:22.306 --> 00:04:33.758
I didn't feel good at all. And I told D, "I feel too sick to go. I don't feel like we should go."And she said, "Okay, well, whatever you want to do, babe,"like she always is—she's always so supportive.

00:04:33.759 --> 00:04:41.039
And I told her, I said, "Let's pray."And the Lord said, "Brandon, it's a healing service.

00:04:41.040 --> 00:04:49.318
Go expect your miracle."And I said, "Yeah, well, duh. We'll go."And so I went and I drove.

00:04:49.319 --> 00:04:53.679
It was a long drive. And I told her, I said, "I'm overcoming so bad right now.

00:04:53.680 --> 00:04:58.037
I'm going to have to pull over to the side of the road."And so I just kept driving by faith.

00:04:58.038 --> 00:05:04.748
I kept standing, I kept quoting the word, I kept believing, just like I teach you all. I was practicing what I preach.

00:05:04.749 --> 00:05:14.194
And I got there expecting, but the first night I did not feel the presence of the Lord as strong as what I was wanting, you know, and I'm not disappointed.

00:05:14.195 --> 00:05:23.420
It's not Billy Burke's fault. No, it's my receptor, where I was at. I'm going into the atmosphere, and it wasn't—you know.

00:05:23.421 --> 00:05:34.556
So the Lord said, "Brandon, I want you to fast."And I said, "You want me to fast?"I said, "Okay, for how long?""Until that night."I said, "Well, that's great.

00:05:34.557 --> 00:05:50.838
Okay, well, I'll do it."So I started praying, I started fasting, and the next morning, I woke up and I went to the service, and the glory came on me, and I felt the power of God hit me.

00:05:50.839 --> 00:05:55.552
I'm telling you, I started feeling all the symptoms start lifting off of me. I started feeling completely healed.

00:05:55.553 --> 00:06:06.594
And I'm telling you, folks, the night before, it was like you could feel it in the atmosphere, and I was hearing it in the spirit realm.

00:06:06.595 --> 00:06:16.762
I don't know if this was something new for me. I told Diana, "This is like something because I'm listening, but I can hear things and what the Lord's showing me.

00:06:16.763 --> 00:06:28.234
Is this fake? This is real. This is what I'm hearing."And you know me, I am so huge on miracles and the glory and the manifestation of everything.

00:06:28.235 --> 00:06:36.079
But I was hearing in the atmosphere the thoughts of—I don't know if it's other people around me or what—"Is this fake?

00:06:36.080 --> 00:06:41.099
Is this made up? Is this performance?"And it was bombarding my thoughts.

00:06:41.100 --> 00:06:47.791
And the Lord said, "Take authority over the atmosphere."And I thought, "That's interesting.

00:06:47.792 --> 00:06:52.103
What are you showing me?"Because you know me, I'm always a student.

00:06:52.104 --> 00:06:57.062
Diana and I are always students. We don't have everything figured out, but we want to learn.

00:06:57.063 --> 00:07:05.662
And I told her, as we're listening and we're hearing, what are we hearing in the spiritual atmosphere of this auditorium right now?

00:07:05.663 --> 00:07:15.090
And I was hearing, "Is this fake? Is this performance? Is this authentic?"All these things. And it was coming, and I personally know this man.

00:07:15.091 --> 00:07:22.590
And I'm like, "Of course it is."And I started coming against that, and I was like, "That is demonic,"but it was coming against your thoughts.

00:07:22.591 --> 00:07:28.088
And as I'm standing in the back, and that's when I went into the next day and it was still lingering.

00:07:28.089 --> 00:07:41.800
That's when the Lord told me, "I want you to fast and pray over this atmosphere."Well, I went in, and we drove around like we do all the time here in Tulsa, driving around our area praying.

00:07:41.801 --> 00:07:48.239
Well, I drove around Fort Worth for about seven hours after the service.

00:07:48.240 --> 00:07:53.476
My goodness, they've got a lot of work to do. I'm not used to a major city like that.

00:07:53.477 --> 00:08:07.936
Sitting in traffic is like going to Tampa, but we were just praying over Fort Worth as we went through there, interceding and praying for the glory to come on that city, praying for a major harvest of souls in the really rough areas.

00:08:07.937 --> 00:08:21.198
Well, as we did that, I started feeling the atmosphere change and was just praying for that meeting that night. When we got to the meeting that night, it was packed.

00:08:21.199 --> 00:08:32.585
But we sat in the back because the Lord said, 'I want you to sit in the back and pray over this service.'So, we sat towards the back, and Diana and I were just interceding.

00:08:32.586 --> 00:08:50.840
We started praying, and you could feel the tangible presence of God; it was so heavy.

00:08:50.841 --> 00:08:59.300
Both of us, at the exact same time, felt a crown, like a glory, come over our heads at the exact same time.

00:08:59.301 --> 00:09:14.952
I looked at her and said, 'I just felt like a helmet of glory came on my head.'And she said, 'Brandon, I felt it too.'It was amazing, and I felt the glory.

00:09:14.953 --> 00:09:22.529
While I was in the back, the Lord said, 'Receive your healing. You don't have to have anybody touch you.

00:09:22.530 --> 00:09:28.648
Practice what you preach.'There are so many people who think you have to have someone lay hands on you to receive. No.

00:09:28.649 --> 00:09:39.345
When you're in the atmosphere of glory, and the presence of the Lord is there, receive what you're believing for. And the Lord said, 'Believe big.

00:09:39.346 --> 00:09:51.323
Believe big.'Even if you're in a service like that and everyone else is getting prayed for, and you feel like you're the only one who isn't, believe God for big things right where you're at.

00:09:51.324 --> 00:09:58.910
I'm telling you, it's time to believe Him for big things—exceedingly, abundantly, above all that you dare ask or think.

00:09:58.911 --> 00:10:03.356
So, I was sitting back, the power of God came on me, and I was healed.

00:10:03.357 --> 00:10:17.718
I'm making this story too long, but after that happened, we were sitting in there and Diana said, 'I can see the mist.

00:10:17.719 --> 00:10:20.639
I can see the mist.'Tell them, babe. Yeah, we were sitting in the very back, and I could see this light mist coming all into the room.

00:10:20.640 --> 00:10:27.560
You know, when you're in that atmosphere and sitting in it, you don't realize it until it's right on you.

00:10:27.561 --> 00:10:40.918
I started looking, and I was like, 'There's a haze in here that wasn't here when we first walked in, right?'And then, all of a sudden, all the fire alarms went off.

00:10:40.919 --> 00:10:46.358
We have video of it. I told Braden to tape it—we can't play it because he doesn't have it downloaded yet.

00:10:46.359 --> 00:10:52.314
But as we could see the mist, the glory, the presence of the Lord started coming in so strong.

00:10:52.315 --> 00:11:02.894
There was a man with cerebral palsy whose hands were all crippled up when he got up there, and the power of God hit his hands and they started straightening out.

00:11:02.895 --> 00:11:14.155
He said, 'I haven't been able to ever do this.'I'm telling you, this guy's faith was off the charts.

00:11:14.156 --> 00:11:28.395
It melted me because here he is, severely handicapped in the natural, giving God praise for where he's at in his life.

00:11:28.396 --> 00:11:46.857
It made me think, 'What do you ever have to complain about when you see somebody overcome?'He was in the midst of his storm, praising God to the point that it challenged me. That was good. It was beautiful.

00:11:46.858 --> 00:11:56.225
We saw so many other people who were believing God for a breakthrough, or for many different things—lumps in their chests and all kinds of things get healed—and it was just wonderful.

00:11:56.226 --> 00:12:11.325
But as those fire alarms were going off, I do have to make a disclaimer here: I do not know what caused the fire alarms to go off in the service, whether somebody pulled the alarm or whatever.

00:12:11.326 --> 00:12:21.013
But we did know before it ever went off, Diana and I both said, 'You can feel the glory; it's in the atmosphere.

00:12:21.014 --> 00:12:33.241
You can see a mist or a fog in here.'Later, the fire alarms started going off all throughout the building, and it was live.

00:12:33.242 --> 00:12:46.549
I told D, 'Did the glory smoke just set off the fire alarm in the church?'I think it did, but you don't want to say that because somebody could have pulled the alarm.

00:12:46.550 --> 00:12:54.875
But between us thousands of people, I want to say it was the glory that set off that fire alarm.

00:12:54.876 --> 00:13:02.686
It was just too cool because I didn't want to be hyperspiritual or try to create sensationalism.

00:13:02.687 --> 00:13:06.886
I just know I'm expecting God to do something big, aren't you?

00:13:06.887 --> 00:13:14.516
I'm expecting God to show up and show off in this month of September.

00:13:14.517 --> 00:13:20.159
The Lord told me as I was sitting there, 'Brandon, what you're seeing is a spiritual arsonist.

00:13:20.160 --> 00:13:46.785
Billy Burke is a spiritual arsonist; he goes and causes fires in these services.'And He said, 'This is what I want you to be—a spiritual arsonist for the Lord, causing fires by the Holy Ghost, stirring people up, and getting them ready for the soon return of the Lord Jesus Christ.'It's time for you to be excited because God is about to show up and show off in your life, and I want you to believe Him for big things tonight.

00:13:46.786 --> 00:13:55.208
I want you to believe Him that what's impossible in your life will soon become possible.

00:13:55.209 --> 00:14:01.902
I'm just believing right now with you for your miracle, for your creative miracle, whatever you may need in your life.

00:14:01.903 --> 00:14:10.550
I told Diana, 'I'm tired of always having this attitude of, well, we're just waiting for it to happen.

00:14:10.551 --> 00:14:25.717
We're ready for the manifestation now.'And Billy Burke said something really cool about it. Braden, tell them what he said about the grocery cart.

00:14:25.718 --> 00:14:35.058
Yeah, the analogy he had was amazing because he was saying how people don't have that bulldog tenacity about their healing and what Jesus did for us on the cross.

00:14:35.059 --> 00:14:40.260
He said whenever you go into a grocery store, you put all your groceries in that cart.

00:14:40.261 --> 00:14:44.151
You don't own the cart, and you don't own the groceries yet—you haven't even paid for them.

00:14:44.152 --> 00:14:53.964
But if somebody walks up and tries to push your cart away, you're like, 'Hey, that's mine!'You will fight them over that, but you don't even own it yet.

00:14:53.965 --> 00:14:58.644
So, that's what he was saying: it's not even yours yet, but Jesus already paid it all.

00:14:58.645 --> 00:15:06.988
Since He paid the price, we should have that same bulldog tenacity of faith over our healing. I thought it was an amazing analogy.

00:15:06.989 --> 00:15:31.518
Even when you don't have the full manifestation yet—it's like you don't have the groceries in your house yet, you just have them in your buggy and you're pushing them around—if someone came up and tried to grab your bread or your eggs out of that cart, you'd go, 'Hey, hold on, those are my eggs!'You haven't even purchased them yet, but you're bold enough to tell people, 'Those are my eggs.'Well, I want you to look at your healing the same way.

00:15:31.519 --> 00:15:41.192
That's my healing. Yes, that's my deliverance. You may not have the full manifestation of what you're believing God for, ladies and gentlemen, but you got to have that.

00:15:41.192 --> 00:15:45.679
That's mine regardless if I'm seeing it or walking in the fruit of it.

00:15:45.680 --> 00:15:52.835
What's in my spiritual cart belongs to me. I have this, and I'm going to walk in it because God paid the price.

00:15:52.836 --> 00:15:58.050
Jesus paid the price for you to walk in total victory in your life.

00:15:58.051 --> 00:16:03.872
He paid the price. Nothing's too big, and nothing's too small. Jesus paid the price for you to have it all.

00:16:03.873 --> 00:16:09.368
And we allow the enemy to come in and try to rob us, even like what I was doing on Wednesday.

00:16:09.369 --> 00:16:15.034
Yeah, I don't want to go to the healing service. I'm overcoming. It's a healing service.

00:16:15.034 --> 00:16:20.952
And I was like, 'You know, okay, believe God in the healing service.'And so we went.

00:16:20.952 --> 00:16:29.405
And so, you know, it's just trying to go through these things and say, 'You know what?

00:16:29.406 --> 00:16:35.500
We got it. We can believe God, too.'Just like this. You know what I'm saying?

00:16:35.501 --> 00:16:44.710
What I'm trying to do is paint it to you all that Brandon and Diana are believing just like you all are. We're just believing for stuff just like you all are.

00:16:44.711 --> 00:16:53.056
And when I'm overcoming in my body, and my flesh wanted to lay in bed and feel sorry for myself, the Lord said, 'I want you to do this.

00:16:53.057 --> 00:17:00.334
I want you to go by faith. I want you to speak to it.'And it wasn't something that was contagious. I was overcoming something with my own flesh.

00:17:00.335 --> 00:17:05.114
And you know, it's like, 'Well, thanks a lot for spreading your bug around.'No, it wasn't a bug.

00:17:05.115 --> 00:17:08.159
It wasn't anything like that. It was something I was overcoming.

00:17:08.160 --> 00:17:11.215
And so I told Diana, I said, 'Let's do this by faith.'And we did it.

00:17:11.216 --> 00:17:15.952
And I got what I was believing for. And it's the glory. The glory.

00:17:15.953 --> 00:17:22.723
And I'm telling you, we're never looking for a person. I'm going to tell you this: it's not the person, it's Jesus.

00:17:22.724 --> 00:17:29.516
And Jesus shows up. And I believe expectation brings the manifestation of what you're believing for.

00:17:29.517 --> 00:17:35.995
And some people get frustrated. They go, 'Oh, you know, I don't like the way he did this.

00:17:35.996 --> 00:17:45.678
I don't like the way...'I don't like the way everybody does everything either, folks, but I'm just believing in an atmosphere of expectation that manifestation is coming.

00:17:45.679 --> 00:17:54.075
I don't care what church it is. You know, I'm just believing God. I'm seeking Jesus at that point, not getting distracted.

00:17:54.076 --> 00:18:02.229
It's like going up, and after we felt the cloud I think, you know, we felt all that glory, and we felt the presence of the Lord so strong.

00:18:02.230 --> 00:18:08.558
I told her, I said, 'I feel like if I wouldn't have come, I would have been so disappointed.

00:18:08.559 --> 00:18:16.060
I would have been so disappointed.'When you have your antenna of expectation up to believe God...

00:18:16.061 --> 00:18:25.759
So, and the other thing was, remember I told you all that we would start to see major generals start to go home.

00:18:25.760 --> 00:18:36.558
And not every single one that goes home is bad. No. Some—and I'm not going to say any of these people are bad, folks, no.

00:18:36.559 --> 00:18:43.930
They've—some of the people that I've seen, because they've opened some doors, they would go home early.

00:18:43.931 --> 00:18:47.420
But that doesn't make you a bad person. That just makes you human, right?

00:18:47.421 --> 00:18:54.125
You know, people mess up. That's what I'm talking about. But in this case, one of—a dear sister—she went home.

00:18:54.126 --> 00:19:01.918
I told you, a prayer general—I'm talking a major, major, huge prayer general—went home yesterday.

00:19:01.919 --> 00:19:10.006
And it went along with what the Lord is showing me about the elders going home and the young generation rising up.

00:19:10.007 --> 00:19:21.171
We have to take the baton of prayer. Everything we do is birthed out of prayer in the spirit realm for these last days in this last revival.

00:19:21.172 --> 00:19:33.012
And that's why the Lord called us. He said, 'Raise up this million men and women prayer army.'And our condolences go out to Patsy Cameneti.

00:19:33.013 --> 00:19:48.994
Her—she went home to be with the Lord, and she was one of Brother Hagin's—he trained her up, and she did prayer at his ministry, and she was a general, and she went home.

00:19:48.995 --> 00:19:56.643
I think she was 67, really too young to go home. 67 years old, and our condolences go out to the family.

00:19:56.644 --> 00:20:02.873
I know it's hard, but I believe we're going to see her sooner than you all realize.

00:20:02.874 --> 00:20:07.512
Yes. For Jesus Christ is coming. Yes. Jesus Christ is coming.

00:20:07.513 --> 00:20:29.474
As I sat there in those services, he said, 'Where's more expectation, the urgency of my return?'We've heard it, and we become so desensitized to, 'Well, yeah, Jesus is coming,'because, you know, the disciples said he was coming and all those people.

00:20:29.475 --> 00:20:38.417
We've heard it for so long, so you become desensitized to the coming of the Lord. You become desensitized because we've heard it so much.

00:20:38.418 --> 00:20:51.994
But the Lord told me, he said, 'You need to have your expectations heightened right now for a major harvest of souls and the glory for the coming of the King.

00:20:51.995 --> 00:21:03.418
For the coming of the King.'I told her, I said, 'I just have—you can sense it in the atmosphere.'September, when we crossed over into September...

00:21:03.419 --> 00:21:07.194
I think tonight's the blood moon, right? Is it tonight, y'all?

00:21:07.195 --> 00:21:14.598
I believe it goes in on the sixth, so it's tomorrow. So, tomorrow night is the blood moon.

00:21:14.599 --> 00:21:27.329
So, then President Trump posted his thing on Truth Social, and he starts telling everybody that he saw that India, Russia, and China are all becoming buddies.

00:21:27.330 --> 00:21:41.952
Now, this is exactly what the Lord told us in 2023. If you remember, he told us this was coming: an alliance with BRICS nations, and then I saw Saudi Arabia coming.

00:21:41.953 --> 00:21:57.439
I saw Venezuela coming. They were going to offer an olive branch of peace to Venezuela to get them out from underneath the Western sanctions and all the stipulations, right?

00:21:57.440 --> 00:22:07.154
But they were trying to back their currency to make it digital, to make it all these things with certain oil and all this different stuff.

00:22:07.155 --> 00:22:23.939
So now we see the United States say, 'Well, it's about drugs, and we're stopping drugs, and we're making a good cause for that.'But the Lord said to us in the last video, there's much more to what's going on with Venezuela than what you can see with the natural eye.

00:22:23.940 --> 00:22:28.986
And when I was typing it out and I told Braden in the post, he said, 'Daddy, what's the title of this?

00:22:28.987 --> 00:22:34.232
You heard it here first.'I'm not talking about out of all the prophetic voices.

00:22:34.233 --> 00:22:40.037
I'm talking about before the news. We're not in competition with prophetic voices.

00:22:40.038 --> 00:22:45.675
We're a family. We have to work together. It's all hands on deck right now.

00:22:45.676 --> 00:22:51.759
And it isn't so-and-so's ministry versus so-and-so's ministry, or this one against that one.

00:22:51.760 --> 00:22:56.260
It's all hands on deck working as a family. We don't have time for pettiness.

00:22:56.261 --> 00:23:02.765
What I'm trying to say is it's before the news. It's before CNN. It's before Fox.

00:23:02.766 --> 00:23:10.691
We told you here first, folks, before Fox talked about it and before CNN talked about it, because we want to become the news.

00:23:10.692 --> 00:23:19.599
The prophetic voice has to rise up and become accurate enough that we're the news, that the spiritual—I told you there's too much spiritual static.

00:23:19.600 --> 00:23:24.556
'Prophet so-and-so says it's September 23rd.'So are you going to combat what he's saying?

00:23:24.557 --> 00:23:29.530
No. God bless him. I'm not here to ever talk that way about another brother.

00:23:29.531 --> 00:23:34.558
Love takes no account of suffered wrong. Love doesn't do that.

00:23:34.559 --> 00:23:38.495
Love believes the best of every person regardless of how it happens.

