00:47:06.537 --> 00:47:12.491
I don't buy any ten-thousand-dollar suit. I'm just saying, listen to me. That's crazy.

00:47:12.492 --> 00:47:24.490
But a majority of you believed it, and we got the emails: "I can't believe you would take the money and go and buy it."I didn't buy anything.

00:47:24.491 --> 00:47:37.001
We just have an amazing—I'm trying to tell you something, this is where I was at with that, warning the people that everything you see on the internet could be fake.

00:47:37.002 --> 00:47:42.113
And having a suit like that happened through the whole video—it never happened.

00:47:42.114 --> 00:47:51.342
No, it never happened. But that's how good AI is getting. It's amazing.

00:47:51.343 --> 00:47:59.030
Braden said, "Hey, Daddy, I can make you wear a kimono. I can make you wear a Chinese kimono-looking thing and wear it.

00:47:59.031 --> 00:48:13.724
It's red. What color do you want it to be, and with what designs?"And he made it on there, and it made me look like I was Asian.

00:48:13.725 --> 00:48:16.788
There you go, thank you, Asian. And it made me look like that. And I said, "That is amazing.

00:48:16.789 --> 00:48:34.337
Look at that, look how clear that is."Yeah, so I'm trying to tell you all, there will be a lot of things that you're going to see in the days ahead that will look real, with alien invasions.

00:48:34.338 --> 00:48:41.271
See, you got me on the right track. This goes right back into the prophetic; we're just so connected.

00:48:41.272 --> 00:48:51.674
But you see, alien invasions are coming that are false. This is demonic.

00:48:51.675 --> 00:48:58.566
What's about to happen is demonic, and you're going to see something that's going to make you think that it's real.

00:48:58.567 --> 00:49:11.526
And what's going to happen is a great deception. You must have your spiritual antennas up, for even the elect will be deceived, if it were possible.

00:49:11.527 --> 00:49:29.118
That's what the scripture says, "if it were possible, even the elect."So that means even the people who think they're the sharpest possible, you're talking about people who think they have a lot going for them spiritually, even they would.

00:49:29.119 --> 00:49:34.436
How is that possible? Because you believed I was wearing a Louis Vuitton suit when I didn't.

00:49:34.438 --> 00:49:43.140
It's becoming clear how it's going to happen. Back twenty years ago, we didn't know.

00:49:43.141 --> 00:49:48.982
We used to think it would be like 3D imaging, like holograms.

00:49:48.983 --> 00:50:00.899
That's what we used to think back in the nineties when I was a kid, or even like Left Behind or Obi-Wan Kenobi, "Help me, Obi-Wan Kenobi, you're our only hope,"with holograms.

00:50:00.900 --> 00:50:17.078
That's what we always thought, but it's going to be so easy now that you can see how they're going to do it. AI, the new industrial revolution, is upon us.

00:50:17.079 --> 00:50:26.043
We pray for Patsy's family, for Mark Hankins and Brenda Hankins and her husband Tom, I think is his name.

00:50:26.044 --> 00:50:31.416
Tom, that's the family. They're going through a lot, and I'm sure they're grieving big time for her.

00:50:31.417 --> 00:50:41.569
We pray for peace that passes all understanding over their hearts, their ministry, and their minds. She was a pillar.

00:50:41.570 --> 00:50:49.675
For somebody to get promoted and go home, they leave that hole, and God's going to raise up new people, but right now they grieve.

00:50:49.676 --> 00:51:02.779
We grieve for that family, and we know that it's hard when you lose somebody right now for this season, when you don't have them here and your heart is heavy.

00:51:02.780 --> 00:51:10.318
So we pray peace for them. It's a comfort for their families during this time. I know it's very hard.

00:51:10.319 --> 00:51:21.277
And I know the Holy Spirit—grandchildren probably—we know the Holy Spirit, when we go through hard times like that, is an ever-present help in a time of need.

00:51:21.278 --> 00:51:27.722
And I believe that for every single one of you. There were people there last night who were grieving over their daughter dying.

00:51:27.723 --> 00:51:44.535
And I prayed over them and prayed for them, you know. People have the valley; He said we would walk through it, He didn't say that we wouldn't experience it at all. In the valley of the shadow of death, we will fear no evil.

00:51:44.536 --> 00:51:54.449
And when you go through those valleys in life, like when we've been with Megan and we see these people and they go, 'Man, we're having all these issues and the valley is hard,'it's real.

00:51:54.450 --> 00:52:07.015
It's real. And I think a lot of times—I don't like the 'spiritual'people, and a lot of times in the circles that we're familiar with, they don't tell you about the struggle that much.

00:52:07.016 --> 00:52:12.780
They don't tell you about how their body is overcoming. They won't even talk about it.

00:52:12.781 --> 00:52:23.118
They won't tell you what's going on with their lives because they don't want to; they don't speak it out, of course. But a lot of times, I feel like it does a disservice.

00:52:23.119 --> 00:52:36.667
You need to know how to believe God through your valley, how to speak to your mountain when you're going through, and the storms of life are coming, and you've got a hurricane all the way around you, and you feel like you're the only one going through it.

00:52:36.668 --> 00:52:39.442
I'm telling you, there's a lot of people going through a lot of stuff.

00:52:39.443 --> 00:52:46.688
They may not always talk about it, but everyone has their stuff.

00:52:46.689 --> 00:52:51.570
Everybody has stuff they're going through. We're still walking through ours.

00:52:51.571 --> 00:52:53.719
We're believing God. Megan's getting better and better, y'all.

00:52:53.720 --> 00:52:56.884
We're believing God for Megan. And there are other things we're believing for.

00:52:56.885 --> 00:53:04.079
Don't sit there and go, 'Well, it's just Megan.'No, we're believing for a lot of things.

00:53:04.080 --> 00:53:13.730
But I want to tell you, after you come across some of the people that we did this week, we're just human just like you all are.

00:53:13.731 --> 00:53:20.141
And we're excited, you're excited, but I want to tell you, we put our pants on just the same way you do.

00:53:20.142 --> 00:53:24.058
We eat the same thing you do. We take a bath because we stink just like you do.

00:53:24.059 --> 00:53:29.624
And I'm going to tell you that if Jesus can do it for us, and where He's brought us out of...

00:53:29.625 --> 00:53:35.199
being where I was, as I was sitting in that auditorium, I used to clean it.

00:53:35.200 --> 00:53:40.639
I would spend hours cleaning it. I would spend hours cleaning all the bathrooms.

00:53:40.640 --> 00:53:46.639
And I glean from where I used to be and where God has brought us now.

00:53:46.640 --> 00:53:50.860
If He could do it for me, ladies and gentlemen, He can do it for you.

00:53:50.861 --> 00:53:59.150
If Jesus can touch my life and turn my mess into a message, I'm telling you, He can turn your mess into a message.

00:53:59.151 --> 00:54:02.591
If you just be willing and obedient, you'll eat the good of the land.

00:54:02.593 --> 00:54:05.301
And I'm telling you, it's where it came from: a seed at a time.

00:54:05.302 --> 00:54:26.489
When we used to say, 'God, if I sow a dollar, if I had a dollar, if I sowed $5, if I had whatever, I believe Him for a harvest to be where I'm at right now.'And it took years, but it's the faith of persistence and saying, 'I believe that God's going to turn this around.'And it doesn't happen overnight a lot of times.

00:54:26.490 --> 00:54:33.940
It's the drip that keeps on dripping on that rock that makes the indentation in a cave over how long?

00:54:33.941 --> 00:54:40.963
A long time. It's the drip that keeps on dripping, one at a time.

00:54:40.964 --> 00:54:46.415
It's how many times you confess it. How many times do you pray over it?

00:54:46.416 --> 00:54:52.558
How many times you keep knocking, you keep pursuing? If you keep seeking, if you keep going...

00:54:52.559 --> 00:55:01.838
and it's like people go, 'Well, I've prayed over it, Brandon, for a couple of days.'Try 25, twenty-some years for something!

00:55:01.839 --> 00:55:04.719
You sit there and you pray over something and you don't see anything.

00:55:04.720 --> 00:55:12.475
For the first couple of years, you're going, 'Man, I know I'm gaining ground,'but you may not see it in the natural too much.

00:55:12.476 --> 00:55:20.959
And then all of a sudden, those roots that went so deep into the ground... I told her, I said, 'It's how long it takes for a bamboo.

00:55:20.960 --> 00:55:26.234
The roots go way down for a long time, and then all of a sudden it has radical growth.

00:55:26.235 --> 00:55:32.163
Radical growth.'But you never see the roots growing down because it's getting a foundation.

00:55:32.164 --> 00:55:35.193
And that's where a lot of you are: you're getting your foundation.

00:55:35.194 --> 00:55:43.199
Your roots are growing down in faith; your roots are growing down, and you're about to see an explosion of growth coming upward.

00:55:43.200 --> 00:55:50.719
Everybody's going to see it overnight, and they're going to say, 'Boy, you are an overnight success.'You say, 'No, you don't know how far my root went down.

00:55:50.720 --> 00:56:01.456
You don't know how far my root went down.'And I'm just going to tell you, it's time for you to not give up on what you've been believing for.

00:56:01.457 --> 00:56:09.005
Be persistent. We are; we're still believing, even in the midst of all our stuff we go through, and people won't have a clue.

00:56:09.006 --> 00:56:18.395
Fight the good fight. This whole thing's new to us—this side of the coin of it, is what I'm going to say.

00:56:18.396 --> 00:56:29.358
We were the grunts for a long time: the janitors, the person counting the offerings, opening the letters and counting the offerings, reading the letters, putting the data in there.

00:56:29.359 --> 00:56:36.221
We did it for twenty-some years. And then to be on this side of it is a lot of spiritual pressure.

00:56:36.222 --> 00:56:41.999
The Lord told me, He said, 'I brought you to another place to die even more.

00:56:42.000 --> 00:56:57.741
You thought you died back there as a janitor; this is even more of a death—dying to self when you feel, "Well, I have this and I have that,"and people should honor that.'And then the Lord said, 'Die to that.

00:56:57.742 --> 00:57:06.200
Die to that. Go back to being like the janitor. You clean and do exactly what I've called you to do.

00:57:06.201 --> 00:57:12.558
Keep cultivating that.'I'm telling you folks, you die at every level.

00:57:12.559 --> 00:57:17.598
You die at every level. Dying to self is what I'm talking about—dying to self.

00:57:17.599 --> 00:57:22.776
And you think, 'Well, I'm going to get over this, and I've got this now,'and the Lord says, 'No, do you see that area right there?

00:57:22.777 --> 00:57:25.793
You're going to have to die a little bit more in that area right there.

00:57:25.794 --> 00:57:30.737
Surrender. Keep surrendering.'But we're going to take communion and pray.

00:57:30.738 --> 00:57:42.495
Do you want to pray with us? You can pray with us. How many people here? Oh, 4,443. Father, we just thank You for the body right now.

00:57:42.496 --> 00:57:51.011
We lift it up before You, Father, and we thank You for all that You've done for us, for this is the meal that heals.

00:57:51.012 --> 00:57:59.598
And we believe, Father, that we receive what we're believing for right now, that by His stripes we're healed.

00:57:59.599 --> 00:58:03.398
Every single one of us, I'm sure, has something we're believing for.

00:58:03.399 --> 00:58:08.264
So, Father, right now, Diana and I are in agreement with them that we'll be there, too.

00:58:08.265 --> 00:58:14.798
That everything they put their hands to will prosper. Everything they touch is overflow.

00:58:14.799 --> 00:58:19.298
Father, this is a season of when You show up and show off in our lives, God.

00:58:19.299 --> 00:58:35.914
And we believe right now in the name of Jesus that we're healed and whole and well in the name of Jesus in every area of our lives—spiritually, physically, financially—and we take this body in the name of Jesus, and we give You all the glory, honor, and praise for it.

00:58:35.915 --> 00:58:43.248
Amen and amen. Thank you, Lord. Now, Lord, we plead the blood of Jesus over us, Father, as we pray.

00:58:43.249 --> 00:58:50.554
We plead the blood over our eyes and over our ears, and over us, that we hear Your voice and a stranger's voice we will not follow.

00:58:50.555 --> 00:58:57.553
We take authority over the demonic spirits that would try to snare us in any way, and we just lift up this time of prayer.

00:58:57.554 --> 00:59:06.892
And we thank You, Lord, that we hear You, and Father, You show us that which is to come in the name of Jesus. And we plead the blood over our sins today, God.

00:59:06.893 --> 00:59:13.645
You said if we confess our sins, you are faithful and just to forgive us of our sins and cleanse us from all unrighteousness.

00:59:13.646 --> 00:59:22.926
And Father, we believe right now in the name of Jesus that all our sins are washed in the blood. And we make much of the blood, and the blood makes much of us.

00:59:22.927 --> 00:59:31.727
And we plead the blood of Jesus over us right now—all around this house, all around our children, all around our finances, all around our car, all around everything.

00:59:31.728 --> 00:59:39.963
I cover us in the blood in the name of Jesus. And I thank you, Lord, for what you've done for us by that blood.

00:59:39.964 --> 00:59:47.873
Amen and amen. That's how we take communion. You say, 'Well, that's not right.'Well, that's how we do it.

00:59:47.874 --> 00:59:55.986
I told Diana when we were praying, we were talking about how the Lord started showing us about prosperity in your soul.

00:59:55.987 --> 01:00:14.260
'Beloved, I wish above all things that you prosper and be in health, even as your soul prospers.'And he said, 'Brandon, you can take herbs, all these things.'He gave us all these different vitamins and all these things at the health food store to try to help us, right?

01:00:14.261 --> 01:00:19.439
But he said, 'You can take that, and take that, and take that, and still be sick because why?

01:00:19.440 --> 01:00:37.468
You're not prosperous in your soul, in your mind, your will, and emotions.''Beloved, I wish above all things that you prosper and be in health, even as your soul prospers.'But if your soul's not prospering, you're not going to be walking in health like you should, because you're always going to have all these issues.

01:00:37.469 --> 01:00:49.279
'And as the man thinketh in his heart, so is he.'And if you're thinking in your heart, you know, you've got anxiety, you've got worry, you've got depression, you've got all this stuff going on, it's affecting your cortisol levels.

01:00:49.280 --> 01:00:55.536
It's affecting all this stuff going on inside of you because you're meditating on the wrong thing.

01:00:55.537 --> 01:01:02.751
And the more you get in this word and you renew your mind by the word of God, this is what's going to change you from the inside out.

01:01:02.752 --> 01:01:09.808
If you get this word down inside of you and you start quoting it, you don't just have it in your thoughts just by your thoughts. Why?

01:01:09.809 --> 01:01:25.838
Because 'as a man thinketh in his heart, so is he.'As you speak it, you're a speaking spirit, speaking that out of your mouth, and you're changing your circumstances because your mountain needs to hear your voice. You have to speak to your mountain.

01:01:25.839 --> 01:01:39.284
So, as you prosper in your soul, as you get the word of God inside of your heart, your mind, your will, and your emotions, and you renew your mind by the word of God, that word's going to change you, and it's going to make you prosperous in your soul.

01:01:39.285 --> 01:01:43.755
It's going to prosper in your mind, your will, and your emotions because you're renewing your mind.

01:01:43.756 --> 01:01:47.511
Because of the washing of the water of the word, you've got to wash your mind.

01:01:47.512 --> 01:01:52.910
You've got to wash it, and you've got to put this on your lips, you've got to put it in your eyes, and it will change you from the inside out.

01:01:52.911 --> 01:02:02.413
And that's why I told her that we were talking about how people are, you know, overcoming, overcoming, overcoming, and you take these things, but you're not getting any better.

01:02:02.414 --> 01:02:07.635
And I'm not ever going to give the glory to an herb. No. But people are always saying, 'I've got this thing right here.

01:02:07.636 --> 01:02:26.464
You take this, and you take that, and whatever, and it's going to make you better.'And they don't get better, and you go, 'Whoa, what's going on?'Well, if you change your thinking, if you change the way you think and get this word down inside of you, it will change you from the inside out.

01:02:26.465 --> 01:02:35.706
That's what I'm trying to tell you. And so as you do that, you become an expert at the word.

01:02:35.707 --> 01:02:46.499
It's like when you go to the gym and you are able to lift five pounds, and then a couple of days later you increase it to ten maybe, and then go to fifteen.

01:02:46.500 --> 01:02:53.713
It's a day-to-day process. It's not just a one and done. It's how many times you dip in that river every day.

01:02:53.714 --> 01:03:00.551
Consistency. Yes. By having those flashcards, Diana... We put the flashcards on the mirror or on your window.

01:03:00.552 --> 01:03:12.418
You could put it wherever you're going to walk and be at the most, at the refrigerator for some, or on your TV.

01:03:12.419 --> 01:03:16.285
On your TV, have scripture, on your remote, on your phone, yeah.

01:03:16.286 --> 01:03:27.439
But whatever it is, let it get through your eyes, wherever the most common place, maybe the bathroom, having it where you see it and you're meditating on that word.

01:03:27.440 --> 01:03:31.101
And it changes you because that's the word that's going to work for you.

01:03:31.102 --> 01:03:51.188
I don't know how many times when we are praying in the spirit and you don't see anything and you're going, 'Man,'and the Lord told me, he said, 'Brandon, if ye abide in me and my words remain in you, you shall ask what you will and it shall be done.'So that's concerning prayer. So if you want your prayer life to change, you have to...

01:03:51.189 --> 01:04:11.038
'If ye abide in me and my words remain in you, you shall ask what you will and it shall be done.'If you don't have your prayer life changing and you don't see manifestation of what you're praying for all the time, find scripture that pertains to what you're believing for and get that in there and put it in the prayer.

01:04:11.039 --> 01:04:24.795
Put it in the prayer. And I've said this before, but you need to know it: 'Faith cometh by hearing, and hearing by the word of God.'And that's the only way you're ever going to get your life changed is by hearing, and hearing by the word of God.

01:04:24.796 --> 01:04:33.764
So you put that word down inside of you, and the more you read it and the more you say it, the more it's going to change because it starts to become rhema to yourself.

01:04:33.765 --> 01:04:48.395
It comes rhema, and it goes... I read scripture and I go, 'Man,'you just know whenever you've got that knowing that you know this scripture has become real to me.

01:04:48.396 --> 01:04:59.752
Ephesians: 'the eyes of your understanding become enlightened to the things of God, to spiritual things.'So I believe with all my heart that's what changes you, and that's what's going to increase your prayer life.

01:04:59.753 --> 01:05:03.865
It's not about praying in tongues all the time or praying in English.

01:05:03.866 --> 01:05:07.862
I prayed, brother, because I told Diana, I said, 'You know, you're always looking for the glory.

01:05:07.863 --> 01:05:16.286
Where is it at with the presence of the Lord?'Because I want to lay hands on people and see them fall out, and the power of God hit them and everything, and you're going, 'Man, Lord, where is that?

01:05:16.287 --> 01:05:22.914
Where is it?'It's getting a foundation of the word inside of you, renewing your mind, getting that inside.

01:05:22.915 --> 01:05:29.519
Because I could pray all day for two hours a day in tongues, three hours a day in tongues, four hours a day, and there is no glory.

01:05:29.520 --> 01:05:41.279
I could read my Bible all the time and read it for hours and hours, and go, 'Well, I have my Bible playing in my head all day long.'But it's the truth, you know, that will set you free.

01:05:41.280 --> 01:05:46.984
It's not about how much scripture you read; it's about how much you retain.

01:05:46.985 --> 01:05:53.912
How much are you retaining? How much are you using against the devil? It's a sword when it comes out of your mouth and you know it.

01:05:53.913 --> 01:06:17.432
When I told you I had that visitation from the devil, and he came in, and I was laying in bed and Diana was asleep, and the whole house lit up like a light bulb with this dingy, dark, evil, and he offered me everything that I could ever dream of—money, finances, boats, houses, everything.

01:06:17.433 --> 01:06:27.993
He said, 'If you serve me and use the gift that you have on your life for seeing, doing things,'he said, 'I'll make you richer beyond your wildest imagination.'He showed me.

01:06:27.994 --> 01:06:34.496
I saw his palace. I saw the throne room. I saw it was black onyx with blood flowing through this thing.

01:06:34.497 --> 01:06:40.691
It was all demonic. This whole experience, I was in the most fear I've ever felt in all my life.

01:06:40.692 --> 01:06:52.719
And I was praying in the spirit. I said, "Shut up,"and he was just laughing at me. He sounded like Michael Jackson off Thriller.

01:06:52.720 --> 01:07:00.714
He was laughing at me because he was offering all this stuff and I said, "I'll never serve you."And it was straight-up demonic, this experience.

01:07:00.715 --> 01:07:11.759
But he was offering all this stuff, right? And as I was praying in the spirit, nothing moved as I was praying.

01:07:11.760 --> 01:07:28.094
But the moment I spoke the word, the moment I started quoting this scripture, the moment I started speaking in tongues and praying in the spirit and adding scripture to it, I started building myself up.

01:07:28.095 --> 01:07:34.716
So praying in the spirit, praying in the spirit, boom, the glory came in and he shot out like a rocket.

01:07:34.717 --> 01:07:45.439
But it wasn't until I got the word down in the prayer that the manifestation of what I was believing for against the demonic happened.

01:07:45.440 --> 01:07:49.595
How many times does it happen over and over and over again? You just pray in the spirit.

01:07:49.597 --> 01:07:52.479
"Oh God, let's pray in the spirit,"just walking around the house.

01:07:52.480 --> 01:07:58.447
"Oh, Father, I thank you concerning my finances. Oh, you're going to supply, Lord."And you're all in worry.

01:07:58.448 --> 01:08:03.693
You're worrying. Take the care out of your prayer. Like Pastor Chip said, take the care out of your prayer.

01:08:03.694 --> 01:08:08.821
And the more you are in care concerning your finances, concerning—well, you know, "I got a bill due.

01:08:08.822 --> 01:08:25.519
I got the light bill due, and I got the rent due, and my baby needs a new pair of shoes."You have all these needs and you're praying the need, and "I've got seed in the ground,"but you're in worry and you're in fear.

01:08:25.520 --> 01:08:29.994
That's why I turn to a scripture and I start renewing my mind to it.

01:08:29.995 --> 01:08:34.960
"God has not given me a spirit of fear, but of power and of love and of a sound mind."2 Timothy 1:7.

01:08:34.961 --> 01:08:42.912
"My God shall supply all my needs according to his riches in glory by Christ Jesus."I started reading those over and over again, and I read Deuteronomy 28.

01:08:42.913 --> 01:08:48.768
I even have it on Deuteronomy 28 right now. That's why as I flip it open, it's my flopping spot.

01:08:48.769 --> 01:08:54.272
It's because it's worn out there because I read it so much. Deuteronomy 28 is my favorite.

01:08:54.273 --> 01:09:03.569
Not the curses part after 16, but the blessing at 13—but I'm just saying, you read about the blessing.

01:09:03.570 --> 01:09:10.675
You read about it, and you meditate on it, and it becomes real to you. So I go around over our eBay totes or whatever I have.

01:09:10.676 --> 01:09:23.809
I use Deuteronomy 28 as my sword coming out of my mouth, believing in my heart that whatsoever things I desire when I pray, I believe I receive them, and I shall have them.

01:09:23.810 --> 01:09:27.544
Mark 11:24. So I'm speaking to the mountain. I'm speaking to that mountain of debt.

01:09:27.545 --> 01:09:33.222
I'm speaking to it and I'm saying, "You have to go."I'm calling those things that be not as though they were.

01:09:33.223 --> 01:09:43.697
I'm calling it in just like you said. The Bible says I can have what the Bible says I can have and I can do what the Bible says I can do.

01:09:43.698 --> 01:09:47.410
There you go. So I'm going to say that. I'm going to believe God in my heart.

01:09:47.411 --> 01:09:50.402
I'm going to say that out of my mouth. I'm going to say Mark 11:24.

01:09:50.403 --> 01:09:56.492
So, I'm going to believe God for this and I'm going to use this scripture and I'm going to pray over my stuff.

01:09:56.493 --> 01:10:00.660
And that's what I do. And like I said, y'all, I'm a work in progress.

01:10:00.661 --> 01:10:02.407
That's what I do for healing. That's what I do for everything.

01:10:02.408 --> 01:10:12.479
And you find it and you go, "God, I'm standing on this because it's a promise."And the more you do that, it becomes more and more real to you every single day.

01:10:12.480 --> 01:10:16.588
And that's what I'm saying. You have to practice. You have to speak the word out of your mouth.

01:10:16.589 --> 01:10:20.010
You have to say it out and believe it in your heart. Don't doubt.

01:10:20.011 --> 01:10:26.305
I said, "I doubt my doubt."I'm not going to sit there and I'm not going to let this doubt rise up on the inside of me.

01:10:26.306 --> 01:10:33.952
Like I told y'all sitting in the back of that church when we went to that healing revival, "This is fake."What?

01:10:33.953 --> 01:10:42.799
That's not my thought, "This is fake. This is put on. This is a performance."That's not where that thought came from.

01:10:42.800 --> 01:10:45.948
That came right out of the pit of hell. That's not the way I believe in my heart.

01:10:45.949 --> 01:10:53.145
But the enemy came in with a whisper. And I was thinking, that sly devil, I have never thought that ever before.

01:10:53.146 --> 01:10:58.702
But it came in like that and tried to drop those thoughts in your head.

01:10:58.703 --> 01:11:07.896
"This healing is not for today."Are you kidding me? Do you see what I'm saying? But he'll come and whisper in your ear.

01:11:07.898 --> 01:11:14.032
But you have to take captive your thoughts, cast down every high imagination that exalts itself above the word of God.

01:11:14.033 --> 01:11:26.336
And so that's what you're going to have to do because if it tried to come against me, folks—and I'll tell you, of anybody, I believe I have seen a lot and I've seen the other side.

01:11:26.337 --> 01:11:31.531
I've seen the silos full of body parts, and you go, "Whoa, I don't believe that."I don't care what you believe.

01:11:31.532 --> 01:11:35.868
I'm trying to tell you something today to help you. You don't want to believe it?

01:11:35.869 --> 01:11:43.014
That's fine, but you're wasting your time on this channel. I'm believing God for it, and I've seen the body parts. I've seen the glory.

01:11:43.015 --> 01:12:02.592
I've seen what's about to take place with the presence that God has for us—a major, major move of God with the pillars of fire, these Shekinah glory spots like Jacob's ladder where there's a major, major move...

01:12:02.593 --> 01:12:16.530
Remember I said this is how it went, and there's a lot of you that are new here, but I saw the Father and he put his hand out, and shafts of light came out of his fingers in this vision that I had.

01:12:16.531 --> 01:12:29.403
And each one of them made a crop—like, you know, like you see these crop circles that are—I believe they were kind of weird, you know, like that's what it looked like, but it was like a harvest area.

01:12:29.404 --> 01:12:33.308
And they were all throughout the United States and around the world, these pillars.

01:12:33.309 --> 01:12:41.996
And they were like Azusa Street revivals, okay? But they were not just one place in California; there were multiple places.

01:12:41.997 --> 01:12:49.794
But they went out of all his fingers, and they were designated areas for major revival, and he called them hot spots.

01:12:49.795 --> 01:12:58.344
Does anybody remember this? Some of you might. But the glory came out of his fingers, and there were pillars of fire.

01:12:58.345 --> 01:13:03.529
And the Lord told me in this, he said, "Do you see those places, Brandon?

01:13:03.530 --> 01:13:17.119
Those are where the end-time revivals, like Holy Ghost Woodstock, are going to take place all around the world."And as the people came into those areas and in those neighborhoods, they fell out in the glory and they were healed.

01:13:17.120 --> 01:13:32.348
And he said before, with Oral Roberts and Jack Coe and all these others, God had to share, kind of like, the glory—He never shares anything—but, you know, people always go, "Oh, brother, you prayed for me and I got healed, right?

01:13:32.349 --> 01:13:46.266
It's because of your ministry."The Lord said, "I'm not going to share my glory with anybody."And you're going to see the demonstrations and manifestations like you have never seen before.

01:13:46.267 --> 01:13:54.072
And as people just show up in these places and just start to worship, the glory came on them and healed them.

01:13:54.073 --> 01:14:03.771
Whatever they needed—I saw limbs coming out, their arms, eyes popping open, ears. I'm talking a major move of God.

01:14:03.772 --> 01:14:11.759
And you know what happened was there were people that were just assigned to be there and say, "This is that.

01:14:11.760 --> 01:14:17.919
God showed up. This is the Lord, the power of the Lord. This is the end time,"you know, like giving them an explanation of how they just got healed.

01:14:17.920 --> 01:14:23.845
So it wasn't just, you know, they went off and didn't have an explanation of what happened to their life.

01:14:23.846 --> 01:14:27.455
That's what I'm trying to say. There was a move of God that happened in those areas.

01:14:27.456 --> 01:14:38.879
And there were people that were assigned to those areas in Branson, and Collinsville, and Minneapolis, and Fort Worth—all these areas where God said, "I'm going to do something like I've never done before.

01:14:38.880 --> 01:14:52.663
Oh, I do a new thing."But who will want to take the land for Jesus in these last days? Well, the elders say, "Well, we've always done it this way.

01:14:52.664 --> 01:15:00.378
We've got to try to hold it back and do it always like this."And the Lord told me, he said, "Brandon, it will be like you've never seen it before.

01:15:00.379 --> 01:15:06.040
It's time to expect something you've never seen before to witness.

01:15:06.041 --> 01:15:11.588
You know, everybody, you get, like I said, people fall out and you don't know if it's real sometimes or not.

01:15:11.589 --> 01:15:24.011
They give you a courtesy fall is what I call them."And they may shake a little bit and you go, "Okay, that's just flesh."But you are about to see something that God is going to show up and show off in your life.

01:15:24.012 --> 01:15:31.568
And you're going to know it's God. You're just going to know. It's authentic.

01:15:31.569 --> 01:15:41.252
It's like we were talking—Diana saw this lady before and she said, "Everybody's just looking for authentic."The world is what I'm talking about.

01:15:41.253 --> 01:15:47.503
The barbers, the beauticians are just looking for authentic. The gas clerks are looking for authentic.

01:15:47.504 --> 01:15:53.956
People in the hood are wanting authentic, a move of God like we've never seen before.

01:15:53.957 --> 01:16:00.568
And it's going to come through a shaking to awaken. It's going to come through a shaking to awaken.

01:16:00.569 --> 01:16:08.158
I saw the Bloods and the Crips and the bikers all coming to the glory of God and at the front of the church and giving their heart to Jesus Christ.

01:16:08.159 --> 01:16:11.083
And the Lord said, "Brandon, they're not just coming in with fishing poles anymore.

01:16:11.084 --> 01:16:22.079
They're coming in by the netfuls."For there will be a moment in time everything will change in a 24-hour period just like it did with 9/11.

01:16:22.080 --> 01:16:29.678
9/11 changed everything. And he said to me, "There's going to be a major event in the spirit realm.

01:16:29.679 --> 01:16:36.280
Everything's going to change."And I have an expectation that it's this year.

01:16:36.281 --> 01:16:48.190
I have an expectation that it's going to be around September the 23rd that we're going to start to see something major.

01:16:48.191 --> 01:16:55.411
He said the people in the days ahead will have to resist healing if they don't want to be healed if they come in these services.

01:16:55.412 --> 01:17:13.740
"I don't want it."Now I don't know what kind of bozo would want to do that, but I'm going to tell you that tapping into the spirit, the Lord said, will be as easy as a bird flies in the air, as a fish swims in the water.

01:17:13.741 --> 01:17:18.722
Brother Hagin gave that word. But the Lord spoke to me, and I didn't even know that Brother Hagin had the word.

01:17:18.723 --> 01:17:28.718
And he said it to me, but he said, "It will be as easy as taking a breath."As easy as taking a breath will be to tap into the anointing and to do things.

01:17:28.719 --> 01:17:34.479
And you're going to see things like you've never seen before.

01:17:34.480 --> 01:17:44.347
So, I just want you all to have—I'm just trying to stir you up a little bit to have that expectation for God to show up in your life.

01:17:44.348 --> 01:17:50.823
There's so many people that are so dry and so thirsty. I've seen it, especially at that meeting this week.

01:17:50.824 --> 01:17:59.434
People are just dry and they're going, "Man, I have all this stuff."And I'm thinking, "Yeah, but Jesus has the answer."Not Brandon, not Diana.

01:17:59.435 --> 01:18:07.618
Jesus has the answer. And there's no shortcuts. There's no cheating.

01:18:07.619 --> 01:18:10.589
You know, like we say, "Well, there's no..."It's like a microwave.

01:18:10.590 --> 01:18:18.289
Everybody thinks it's a microwave. No, it's an Easy-Bake Oven.

01:18:18.290 --> 01:18:25.820
It's your slow cooker, and you've got to put it in the scripture. You've got to put it in. And it's not a one-and-done.

01:18:25.821 --> 01:18:38.319
How bad do you want your life to change and go from glory to glory and not be the same anymore? Well, you can't be spiritually lazy.

01:18:38.320 --> 01:18:48.959
"Well, you know, I tried it a couple times and I read my Bible one time, brother, and I didn't see change."It's consistency.

01:18:48.960 --> 01:18:52.498
How bad do you want change? And you see it a little bit at a time.

01:18:52.499 --> 01:19:00.922
First you see the blade, then you see the ear, then you see the full manifestation, but you've got to water it, and you've got to nurture it.

01:19:00.923 --> 01:19:10.158
Just like a farmer prays over his crops. I'm sure he's out there going, "Man, I need that corn to get up."But he's not stressing out unless there's a drought.

01:19:10.159 --> 01:19:16.399
He just knows that he planted the seed and he's believing God for the increase.

01:19:16.400 --> 01:19:23.279
And he's out there and he checks on it, making sure the crows are not in it or whatever.

01:19:23.280 --> 01:19:29.123
So, you've got to maintain your seed. That's what I'm trying to say. You've got to quote the word over it. You've got to pray.

01:19:29.124 --> 01:19:35.190
You've got to go out there and maybe put some spiritual Roundup on some weeds, casting down some stuff.

01:19:35.191 --> 01:19:40.771
"I bind you in the name of Jesus off my harvest. You let it go, devil, in the name of Jesus.

01:19:40.772 --> 01:19:44.820
I call those things that be not as though they were."And I say, "I'm blessed in the city.

01:19:44.821 --> 01:19:49.678
I'm blessed in the field. I'm blessed coming in and I'm blessed going out.

01:19:49.679 --> 01:19:55.742
I'm healed in my body. I'm delivered in my body. I'm not moved by what I see. I'm not moved by what I feel.

01:19:55.743 --> 01:20:02.079
I'm moved by what the word of God says."And He said, "By His stripes, I am healed.

01:20:02.080 --> 01:20:09.789
He was wounded for my transgressions. He was bruised for my iniquities.

01:20:09.790 --> 01:20:19.776
The chastisement of our peace was upon Him, and with His stripes, we are healed."See, even I get it—I've quoted that probably two or three thousand times or more, and I mess up right then.

01:20:19.778 --> 01:20:25.921
See, it's real. But you just keep going. And I'm not kidding, that's one of my favorite verses.

01:20:25.922 --> 01:20:35.058
You just keep going over it and over and over and over it. So, what are they saying in the comment section?

01:20:35.059 --> 01:20:44.313
Yes, they memorize Psalms 24 and 93. Yeah, Psalm—yeah, "I pray deep roots in my spirit."Psalms 91, mhm, Psalms 23.

01:20:44.314 --> 01:20:53.027
I told you in the days ahead, if you don't have it in your heart, there's a lot of you that will not make it in the days ahead for what I've seen coming.

01:20:53.028 --> 01:21:01.874
And I don't say that to scare you. I say that to prepare you. You need to know a great shaking is coming.

01:21:01.875 --> 01:21:08.923
I'm just being real with y'all. There's a major shaking that's about to take place beyond anybody's comprehension.

01:21:08.924 --> 01:21:18.636
And the Lord told me, he said, "You must remain filled with the Holy Spirit like you've never been before.

01:21:18.637 --> 01:21:24.268
Being filled, being filled. Do not become spiritually dry."Yeah, I'm complacent.

01:21:24.269 --> 01:21:30.428
"Drink, drink, drink."I even told a prophetic friend, "You're dumping out, dumping out, and dumping out all the time.

01:21:30.429 --> 01:21:36.896
You're dumping out, sir. But the Lord told me to call and tell you, you need to drink, drink, drink.

01:21:36.897 --> 01:21:43.098
You can dump out and tell everybody about Jesus all the time, but your water level gets low.

01:21:43.099 --> 01:22:03.585
You get out there and you're just talking out of dryness."And the Lord told me you have to take times of refreshing and drink, drink, and have that spiritual Holy Ghost thermostat inside because with our flesh, you know when it's time to eat.

01:22:03.586 --> 01:22:18.311
Your body tells you, or you'll wake up and you'll say, "I feel like my mineral levels are low,"or you think, "I need to take a certain vitamin,"or you think, "I haven't gone to the bathroom in a while,"so you take something for that.

01:22:18.312 --> 01:22:32.529
But it's just using the Holy Spirit to say—the Holy Spirit tells you, "Your worship level's low, your word level's low,"and just following the Holy Ghost.

01:22:32.530 --> 01:22:44.597
Your flesh tells you, "I'm cold, I need a jacket."Your spirit's speaking, but you've killed it because you haven't taken care of it.

01:22:44.598 --> 01:22:48.584
Your flesh gets usually three meals, two meals maybe, and some snacks a day.

01:22:48.585 --> 01:22:55.198
You listen to your flesh the moment it starts speaking. Yes, people don't listen to the Holy Spirit.

01:22:55.199 --> 01:23:04.593
No, but your spirit—you're a speaking spirit. I'm telling you, the spirit realm is more real than the natural.

01:23:04.594 --> 01:23:09.720
But just because you can't see it... But the moment is it. Tell them more. Yes.

01:23:09.721 --> 01:23:20.035
So a lot of times I'll wake up and I've been in the word a lot, but the next day I'll be like, I'll hit that, you know, where you're like, "I need something."What is it?

01:23:20.036 --> 01:23:26.050
And the Holy Spirit rises up in me and he'll say, "Diana, you need to get in worship today.

01:23:26.051 --> 01:23:32.408
Get in worship."And then sometimes he'll say, "You need to praise more,"because I've been in worship so long and he'll say, "Praise.

01:23:32.409 --> 01:23:39.590
You need to praise."So then, you know, sometimes it'll be just using him as a gauge.

01:23:39.591 --> 01:23:45.678
The Holy Spirit tells you where to go day to day. It's custom for you.

01:23:45.679 --> 01:24:03.359
And so, because he's here to lead and guide us into all truth, he's directing us to Jesus, constantly saying, "Today you need the word, Diana, for your circumstance, what you're going through today, what you're feeling."Because we all wake up with these feelings and you're thinking, "What is this that I'm feeling?

01:24:03.360 --> 01:24:10.918
How do I get through this?"You're thinking, "How do I keep fighting this good fight of faith?"And he's there to lead and guide us, and we use him.

01:24:10.919 --> 01:24:16.238
We use discernment. He's there to help us. He's our helper. He comes to our aid.

01:24:16.239 --> 01:24:20.096
So that's just how we keep on fighting the good fight of faith.

01:24:20.097 --> 01:24:24.399
We find His grace to keep going. That's how we go. That's exactly right.

01:24:24.400 --> 01:24:29.279
And if you don't do that, you're going to be a spiritual wimp. Yes.

01:24:29.280 --> 01:24:36.833
And when the devourer comes to your house and starts knocking on your door, he'll come in and eat you.

01:24:36.834 --> 01:24:46.446
Yeah. But the Bible says the enemy comes in like a roaring lion. He's walking about seeking whom he may devour, right?

01:24:46.447 --> 01:24:55.381
And the only one that he can devour is the one that's not being spiritually up on their game.

01:24:55.382 --> 01:24:59.517
And a lot of people won't even let their hunger level go for their flesh that long.

01:24:59.518 --> 01:25:06.457
So, at that first sign of hunger, like that stomach growling, they're like, "I need food."So they go and eat right away.

01:25:06.458 --> 01:25:19.242
But when you have that first—just that, because the Holy Spirit is such a gentleman, and it's just that still small voice inside of you, and that leading, he leads you and you feel that pull, that inward tug to go, "This is what you need.

01:25:19.243 --> 01:25:26.791
This is the direction you should go today."And whenever you yield to that, and you yield to him, then it grows.

01:25:26.792 --> 01:25:30.314
It grows and grows and grows in you because you're yielding to it.

01:25:30.315 --> 01:25:41.913
So, just like you yield to the flesh and you say, "I need food."At the first sign, you don't even let it go very long to that full-blown rumbling hunger.

01:25:41.914 --> 01:25:50.486
It's just that first little shakiness and you're like, "Oh, I need food."So, it's the same way with your spiritual side.

01:25:50.487 --> 01:25:58.856
At that first sign, you say, "This is what I need. I'm yielding to the Holy Spirit."You're yielding to him constantly.

01:25:58.857 --> 01:26:05.056
Just as you feel that shakiness and say, "I need food,"you yield to the Holy Spirit.

01:26:05.057 --> 01:26:09.238
And how do you become familiar? How do you know what you need, though?

01:26:09.239 --> 01:26:14.739
Well, the more you yield to him, the more you know. He'll lead and guide you. Yeah.

01:26:14.740 --> 01:26:24.879
It's more like, "How do I know I need this drink of water versus maybe some vegetables?"You just know hunger versus thirst.

01:26:24.880 --> 01:26:33.453
There are things in the spirit: "I'm thirsty. I'm hungry."You'll learn to develop your spirit, and you'll go right now.

01:26:33.454 --> 01:26:40.457
Drinking of the water of the word, eating of the meat of the word, worship and praise.

01:26:40.458 --> 01:26:50.678
You're drinking and filling yourself back up, and you get into that flow where you're feeding your spirit. You're drinking, and you're strong.

01:26:50.679 --> 01:27:00.057
And when the devil comes up there like a roaring lion, seeking whom he may devour, he comes to your house and he goes, "I got to get out of here."You know why?

01:27:00.058 --> 01:27:07.410
Because he knows that you've got your full armor on. You've got your sword of the Spirit, and you're ready to cut his head off like Goliath.

01:27:07.412 --> 01:27:15.312
And he's going, "I came to the wrong house today."Yes. "I came to the wrong house today.

01:27:15.313 --> 01:27:21.219
You better not mess with me."Yeah. "Don't be coming to my door."And he runs off.

01:27:21.220 --> 01:27:25.798
But he's only going to run off if you've got your armor on and you know who you are.

01:27:25.799 --> 01:27:35.389
If you've just got your sword up there and maybe nothing else on, he goes, "Ah, I've got dinner today."Yeah.

01:27:35.390 --> 01:27:44.959
I mean, you know, he's the big bad wolf. So, and like I said, I don't ever really talk about the devil very often.

01:27:44.960 --> 01:27:48.409
I don't give him any place. I give no place to the devil by talking about him.

01:27:48.410 --> 01:27:51.798
I really don't. I don't even talk about that story I just told you all very often.

01:27:51.799 --> 01:28:01.447
But because I don't allow him to try to get that much real estate in my mind, meditating on him and thinking about him—he's defeated.

01:28:01.448 --> 01:28:07.822
Yes. So, why would you talk about somebody who's already been defeated that much?

01:28:07.823 --> 01:28:22.155
I remind him of his defeat and I remind him of his future all the time, but I'm not going to give him real estate in my mind to sit there and start because he's not paying rent, you know, by tormenting.

01:28:22.156 --> 01:28:29.119
Fear has torment. And he'll always try to play fear's greatest hits: "The what-ifs.""What if?

01:28:29.120 --> 01:28:36.137
What if? What if?"You know, he comes up there and puts his greatest hits in your mind all the time.

01:28:36.138 --> 01:28:41.519
"What if? What if this happens? What if that?"And it continually bombards your thoughts.

01:28:41.520 --> 01:28:43.593
And those are the thoughts of fear coming against your head.

01:28:43.594 --> 01:28:49.919
And that's why I told Diana, I said, "I don't know, he's trying to come in."Well, my word level is low.

01:28:49.920 --> 01:28:58.314
I've got to spend more time in the word today. So, I don't know, hopefully this is helping you all.

01:28:58.315 --> 01:29:06.833
We try to give you things that we work through. And Diana and I, like I said, we're a work in progress, but this is how we get through it.

01:29:06.834 --> 01:29:13.389
Yes. And we're a work in progress just like everybody else. But I'm going to tell you, this is where I see fruit.

01:29:13.390 --> 01:29:21.377
And if you listen to what we're telling you, you don't have to go around the mountain fifty billion times until you catch on and get a hold of something.

01:29:21.378 --> 01:29:31.359
I said, "Well, I wish somebody, when Megan was first diagnosed with autism, I just wish somebody that was a veteran in this could have come by and told us, 'Don't go down this road.

01:29:31.360 --> 01:29:38.434
Don't go down that road,'because we did it by trial and error."And what we're telling you right now is years and years and years of experience.

01:29:38.435 --> 01:29:46.138
And you say, "Well, that's simple."Well, to a baby Christian, it isn't. To somebody who's just trying to figure it out.

01:29:46.139 --> 01:29:55.474
Heartache is how we learned it—years and years of just getting a hold of the word and saying, "Listen, we're going to live this out. We're going to walk by faith and not by sight.

01:29:55.475 --> 01:30:02.253
I'm going to live, and I'm going to be on the victory side of things."It's like we heard, "Better to stumble in faith than to sit in doubt."Yeah.

01:30:02.254 --> 01:30:11.970
It's my new favorite thing. I heard it from Billy Burke. He said, "Better to stumble in faith than to sit in doubt."And I said, "Oh, that is so good."Run with that.

01:30:11.971 --> 01:30:21.881
So good. Yeah. I like it. Say it again. That's a t-shirt. "Better to stumble in faith than it is to sit in doubt."Yeah.

01:30:21.882 --> 01:30:28.465
Oh, man, that got me all fired up when I was sitting there. I am not going to sit.

01:30:28.466 --> 01:30:38.799
I'd rather stumble in faith than to sit in doubt. I'm not going to sit there and just be a whiner about things. It's not going to change anything.

01:30:38.800 --> 01:30:43.980
Feeling down about yourself and feeling like, "Oh, I can't get through this,"it's not going to change anything.

01:30:43.981 --> 01:30:52.439
And, quite frankly, nobody really cares. I'll be real. If you're the only one wallowed in self-pity, it isn't going to get any better.

01:30:52.440 --> 01:30:58.833
The only thing that's ever going to get you out of that self-pity and depression is the word of God.

01:30:58.834 --> 01:31:03.293
You can go to a counselor, but guess what? They're waiting for the next check.

