And that's why I'm just being real with y'all. I'm just being transparent. I'm trying to help you, so you go from glory to glory.

02:15:38.560 --> 02:16:04.314
No matter how big Jesus uses you—like a Billy Graham level or a Reinhard Bonnke or whatever, you know what I'm saying, somebody who had millions of people watch them in an audience—it all comes through refining, is what I'm trying to tell you.

02:16:04.315 --> 02:16:07.519
I'm talking about: it all comes from... It's the small foxes.

02:16:07.520 --> 02:16:12.218
The Lord even showed me this: it's the small foxes that ruin the vine.

02:16:12.219 --> 02:16:17.845
It's the little things. It's the small foxes. It's not the great big things.

02:16:17.846 --> 02:16:24.553
You think it's the big thing. No, it's the small things. So, all right.

02:16:24.555 --> 02:16:34.669
Did you put more water in my chicken? Yeah, you did. Just put some more in there. I know I had it on slow cook. No, you're good.

02:16:34.670 --> 02:16:38.873
I just want to make sure because I know this is going way long and I was making sure it's all clean and going.

02:16:38.874 --> 02:16:46.392
It's 11 o'clock. All right. Let's pray a little bit here. Okay. Did that help them? I don't know.

02:16:46.393 --> 02:16:50.075
I try to tell them how I'm going through it, to make sure they're getting it.

02:16:50.076 --> 02:16:54.931
So, if they can listen to me—man, if I can help them get through it so you don't have to live it.

02:16:54.932 --> 02:17:02.175
I don't have anybody coaching me. You know, you got little pieces of puzzles and I grab from everybody I can.

02:17:02.176 --> 02:17:14.791
And I'm going, 'If I can glean a little bit of this over here and I glean a little bit over here from this general or whoever...'and you go, 'Hey,'but there's not a lot of people just sitting down saying, 'Hey, I want to pour into you, Brandon.'You know what I'm saying?

02:17:14.792 --> 02:17:18.539
I'm going to tell you, it has not been that way for Brandon Biggs.

02:17:18.540 --> 02:17:23.183
Everybody's saying, 'We see your platform. We want to help you.'They don't.

02:17:23.184 --> 02:17:28.622
Most people want to take from you, but the ones that you want to glean from don't have time for you.

02:17:28.623 --> 02:17:38.116
And you go, 'Okay, that's fine. Die to it. I don't need the general to give me wisdom. I need Jesus.'Do you get what I'm saying?

02:17:38.117 --> 02:17:51.678
I hope y'all are hearing me because a lot of you—I hear you in the emails and in person this week, saying, 'Please, please, please, please.'And I'm like, 'No, I didn't have nobody.

02:17:51.679 --> 02:18:04.689
Nobody. Nobody was there.'We were sitting by ourselves for 10 years—10 years in our home, in an 800-square-foot house, watching YouTube videos, feeding ourselves.

02:18:04.690 --> 02:18:13.192
And nobody was there. Nobody. Most people when we went in there, Megan was so disruptive they'd ask you to leave: 'Please take her out.

02:18:13.193 --> 02:18:20.756
You're disrupting the service.'And she would wet on their chairs or do whatever, and you would go, 'Okay, what's even the point?

02:18:20.757 --> 02:18:32.585
It's embarrassing.'And so, we just watched YouTube videos, read our Bibles together, and prayed, cultivating this by ourselves with nobody even caring most of the time.

02:18:32.586 --> 02:18:37.618
They didn't even call and check on you. No family. No, it was terrible.

02:18:37.619 --> 02:18:42.695
And you think, 'Well, I need this person to acknowledge me.'They won't.

02:18:42.696 --> 02:18:49.196
And even at this level, they still don't. They still don't. They don't care.

02:18:49.197 --> 02:18:56.509
And I'm not mad about it. It's okay because He is the one that's in control. Do you get that?

02:18:56.510 --> 02:19:08.525
I try to help you all because you all believe, 'Well, when you get to this level, more people will pour into you and help you.'No. No, that's not true. No.

02:19:08.526 --> 02:19:24.451
Jesus is there just like He was back in the 800-square-foot house, sitting on a couch, praying with snakes crawling in because you live in the poverty area and you think, 'Man, nobody cares,'and then Jesus comes and shows up.

02:19:24.452 --> 02:19:38.441
It wasn't nobody that gave Brandon Biggs YouTube. I had people tip their hat toward me and say, 'Hey, we want to do a collab with you,'but once you get like 5,000 subscribers or whatever, it's Jesus.

02:19:38.442 --> 02:19:45.518
Do you understand? So that's who will show up in your life. You don't need your pastor to tip his hat to you.

02:19:45.519 --> 02:19:55.279
You don't need an evangelist. You don't need whoever. You just need to stay and do exactly whatever He says to do—do it.

02:19:55.280 --> 02:20:01.358
Does that make sense to you? Whatever He tells you to do, do it.

02:20:01.359 --> 02:20:12.440
Remember Mary told the people with the water pots—and she spoke to me, saying, 'Whatever He tells you to do, do it.'Well, how's He going to turn water into wine?

02:20:12.441 --> 02:20:19.875
I don't know. But whatever He tells you to do, do it. He can take something and make it into a lot of something.

02:20:19.876 --> 02:20:25.999
He can take the fish and the loaves and give twelve baskets of overflow.

02:20:26.000 --> 02:20:29.782
When He tells you to give, give. When He tells you to sleep, sleep.

02:20:29.783 --> 02:20:37.119
When He tells you to march, march. Whatever He tells you to do, do it.

02:20:37.120 --> 02:20:42.569
Sit on the back row. 'Well, that don't make no sense. Don't you think I should be...'Nope.

02:20:42.570 --> 02:20:49.788
Sit. Pray. 'Well, we got a seat.'Nope. Pray, fast. Whatever He tells you to do, do it.

02:20:49.789 --> 02:20:55.599
It's the path to the greater glory. And I'm telling you, this is one of my things: my weight.

02:20:55.600 --> 02:20:59.700
You want to talk about my greater glory, how to go there? Deal with your fat self.

02:20:59.701 --> 02:21:11.444
I'm just being real with y'all. It's me. Hey, when I get under stress, I eat too many potato chips. I eat too much ice cream because it's a stress reliever.

02:21:11.445 --> 02:21:21.449
And you think, because it's not sin in the natural—because you're not looking at bad stuff on the internet, you're not drinking, you're not cussing, you're not doing bad things—that that's okay because it qualifies.

02:21:21.450 --> 02:21:25.438
But the Lord said, 'I want you to take better care of your health.

02:21:25.439 --> 02:21:38.318
Stop eating all that fast food and the trash you put in there.'And I said, 'Where's the greater glory?''The refiner's fire is back there, buddy.

02:21:38.319 --> 02:21:54.810
You remember when I told you to lose 80 pounds again?''Yeah, I remember that.''Well, your refiner's fire is your weight. You have an issue with potato chips.

02:21:54.811 --> 02:22:05.992
You need to get that under control and get the Word underneath that.'And I say, 'Uh...'and I don't want any of y'all poking at me with an email saying, 'Brandon, you don't look like you lost weight.'I'm doing the best I can.

02:22:05.993 --> 02:22:10.110
I'm working on it. I'm telling you, some people's refiner is different than others.

02:22:10.111 --> 02:22:15.499
And you go, 'Well, I'm a fitness instructor. I don't have to.'Well, guess what? He's going to get you somewhere there.

02:22:15.500 --> 02:22:21.531
If you want to go in the greater glory, your refiner—you probably have a pride problem, and He's going to tell you to go clean poop, too.

02:22:21.532 --> 02:22:25.999
So, just telling you the truth. It's not something you're going to be good at.

02:22:26.000 --> 02:22:30.794
It's something that makes you sharpen in that area. It could be pride.

02:22:30.795 --> 02:22:35.962
It probably is for everybody. Yes, yes, that's what I'm trying to say.

02:22:35.963 --> 02:22:44.559
He might tell you to do something else. I don't know. But whatever it is, do it and you'll go through the refiner.

02:22:44.560 --> 02:22:54.128
So I say, 'Okay, Lord, here am I.'So I go and get my little Subway six-inch sub, or whatever I've got to have for the day.

02:22:54.129 --> 02:23:04.982
And He said, 'I just want you to eat that many calories today.'I said, 'Lord, but the cookie people just sent some cookies in the mail.'And, you know, I got...

02:23:04.983 --> 02:23:09.565
and I'm not kidding you, the devil sent those cookies. I know he did, because I made a covenant.

02:23:09.566 --> 02:23:18.236
I told the Lord. And we got this big old box of cookies from some friends, and it was beautiful cookies. Really good ones. Gourmet.

02:23:18.237 --> 02:23:37.272
And I was looking at it, and Diana goes, 'You'll never believe what's in that box after the conversation we had last night.'I said, 'What?'She goes, 'These are gourmet cookies.'And I go, 'Get thee behind me, Satan!'I tell you what, I was so irritated because I was looking at those, because it's my thing.

02:23:37.273 --> 02:23:52.318
And I got this beautiful package, and they're sitting in there, and I thought, 'I cannot believe this.'But then I can, because it's the refining.

02:23:52.319 --> 02:24:01.298
It's just being real with y'all. I try to... And those cookies are for the kids. Yeah. So, I said, 'Here, Paisley. Here, Megan.

02:24:01.299 --> 02:24:08.817
If you want a little cookie every once in a while, here's you a cookie.'So, I'm not going to try to tell them to eat them all, but I'm just saying, it's the dealing with the greater glory.

02:24:08.818 --> 02:24:22.879
So, there you go. I'm trying to help you. All right. Father, I just thank you for everything you do for us that takes us from glory to glory.

02:24:22.880 --> 02:24:26.957
Father, every person who's here tonight has something they're going through.

02:24:26.958 --> 02:24:31.975
And the refining changes them. And I thank you, Father, for the refining.

02:24:31.976 --> 02:24:42.693
I thank you, Father, that just like we read in the Word, the refining takes us from glory to glory. Not anything else. It's the potter's will.

02:24:42.694 --> 02:24:48.121
We have this treasure in earthen vessels, that the excellency of the power will be known to Him and not of us.

02:24:48.122 --> 02:24:52.219
So, Father, I thank You, Lord, for every single one of them tonight.

02:24:52.220 --> 02:25:05.839
We lift them up before You, Father, that they go through what they need to go through, whatever their flesh is lacking in, Father, so that they're able to go from glory to glory with refining fire.

02:25:05.840 --> 02:25:10.296
Father, I pray healing over their bodies tonight. I pray deliverance over their bodies.

02:25:10.297 --> 02:25:20.797
Father, I thank You that by Your stripes they are healed, whole, and delivered in the name of Jesus. We thank You, Lord, that they're set free by the blood.

02:25:20.798 --> 02:25:31.412
We thank You, Lord, that they're prosperous and everything they put their hands to, everything they touch is blessed—in the city, in the field, coming in, and going out.

02:25:31.413 --> 02:25:40.239
I thank You, Lord, that this is a time like never before that they'll excel, that the sowers and the reapers will go hand in hand.

02:25:40.240 --> 02:25:44.197
And we believe it, Father, that today's the day for great change.

02:25:44.198 --> 02:25:49.919
We believe, Father, that their life is going to change on a dime.

02:25:49.920 --> 02:25:54.514
Father, I thank You, Lord, for their marriages, Father, right now in the name of Jesus.

02:25:54.515 --> 02:26:00.768
Father, their marriages are blessed, their marriages are strong, and, Father, they get along.

02:26:00.769 --> 02:26:14.173
And Father, I thank You, Lord, that they'll not have strife in their homes, that their homes are homes of peace, that they have great joy in their houses, and that, Father, in this time of the end times, Father, they're more heightened.

02:26:14.174 --> 02:26:19.890
They're seeking You. They have eyes, and their antennas are up.

02:26:19.891 --> 02:26:23.437
They're hearing You, and a stranger's voice they'll not follow.

02:26:23.438 --> 02:26:28.672
We believe, Father, right now with them that they're hearing You in a greater capacity.

02:26:28.673 --> 02:26:39.358
May the blood of Jesus Christ cover them, and everything they do, they do all to the glory of God.

02:26:39.359 --> 02:26:48.403
Thank You, Father. We thank You, Lord. We thank You for our friends, for all the people that come and watch us on a day-to-day basis.

02:26:48.404 --> 02:26:55.465
We thank You, Lord, that they spent their night with us and that they're expecting God to show up and show off in these last days.

02:26:55.466 --> 02:27:09.839
As we see the eclipse tomorrow, Father, as we see this eclipse, we know this is a sign, for the coming of the Lord Jesus Christ is getting so close.

02:27:09.840 --> 02:27:14.471
We give You all the glory, honor, and praise. Father, we thank You. They're delivered in their bodies.

02:27:14.472 --> 02:27:27.919
They're healed, whole, and well in everything they have need of in the name of Jesus.

02:27:27.920 --> 02:27:33.592
How long has this been going? Two hours and 30 minutes. Two hours and 30 minutes.

02:27:33.593 --> 02:27:39.378
We can do another one tomorrow. I should have prayed more, but I had things on my heart to talk about.

02:27:39.379 --> 02:27:44.713
And you say, "You talked too much."Well, yeah, I probably did, but I want to pray more.

02:27:44.714 --> 02:27:50.022
I should have prayed more, but now it's three hours. I know, I've got my chicken in there.

02:27:50.023 --> 02:28:00.478
But we just want to tell you we love you. Thank you for joining us, talking, and hearing me ramble for two hours and 30 minutes.

02:28:00.479 --> 02:28:07.999
Hopefully, you got something out of that. You know, I believe there's a lot there, that I fed you a lot really quick.

02:28:08.000 --> 02:28:15.912
You know, you can use it, rewind it, and do whatever, and hopefully it changes you from glory to glory, because that's what I'm doing.

02:28:15.913 --> 02:28:23.019
So, but we love you and pray. We're excited for all the salvations tonight, and we'll come back and pray probably tomorrow.

02:28:23.020 --> 02:28:30.932
I know I was planning to dip in the river. I didn't. I know two and a half hours is a long time, but it's going on pretty late here.

02:28:30.933 --> 02:28:34.754
But we love you all, and we're so grateful for every single one of you.

02:28:34.755 --> 02:28:41.474
Thank you for being with us, and we'll come back again and do the prayer time, and next time I won't talk at all.

02:28:41.475 --> 02:28:49.593
I'll just pray. Jesus loves you, and we love you. Remember, put a smile on your face and a song in your heart.

02:28:49.594 --> 02:28:58.880
Jesus loves you. We love you. Bye-bye. And have a wonderful night. Bye-bye.

